<para style="q1">

<verse number="3" style="v" />Come look at the complete ruins,</para>

<para style="q1">all the damage that the enemy has done in the holy place.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="4" style="v" />Your adversaries roared in the middle of your appointed place;</para>

<para style="q1">they set up their battle flags.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="5" style="v" />They hacked away with axes</para>

<para style="q1">as in a thick forest.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="6" style="v" />They smashed and broke down all the engravings;</para>

<para style="q1">they broke them with axes and hammers.</para>
